config HY310_CPU_COMM
	tristate "HY310 CPU_COMM — ARM/MIPS IPC Framework"
	depends on OF
	help
	  Inter-processor communication framework for the HY310 projector.
	  Enables ARM ↔ MIPS display co-processor communication via shared
	  memory and hardware mailbox. Required for display output control.

	  Based on reverse engineering of Allwinner HAL_SX6 cpu_comm framework
	  from the stock H713 firmware.

	  If unsure, say Y.
